                        <desc>
                          <locus target="#iv(erso)" facs="002">Fol. iv(erso)</locus>, in a crude hand in pencil: Hymn to the Archangel Gabriel
                        </desc>
                        </item>

                      <item xml:id="a2">
                        <desc>
                          <locus target="#127v" facs="130"> f. 127v, col.1</locus>: <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3108RepCh388">Yǝweddǝsǝwwa
